Copyright (C) Nathan Moinvaziri and contributors.
Portions based on the original minizip by Gilles Vollant.

NOTE: This is a vendored copy of minizip-ng (v4.2.1) that has been ALTERED for
NeatZip (CleanZipKit): patched to support raw ZIP entry writes / AES key
injection for the parallel libdeflate pipeline. Per condition 2 below, this
altered source is plainly marked as such; the patch is tracked in the project
history (prototype/minizip-ng.patch).

